1. *Muškarac* je priroda stvorio sa više snage. (Man was created by nature with more strength.)
2. On je *muškarac* koji je uvek spreman da pomogne drugima. (He is a man who is always willing to help others.)
3. *Muškarčevo* delo je obeležilo istoriju. (The work of a man has marked the history.)
4. *Muškarci* su se okupili da podrže jedni druge. (Men gathered to support each other.)
5. Ona je bila oduševljena *muškarcem* koji je ušao u sobu. (She was delighted by the man who entered the room.)